
Code and data for the paper "Joint Video Summarization 
and Moment Localization by Cross-Task Sample Transfer."

<br/>
python version: 3.6.6
<br/>
pytorch version: 1.0.1
<br/>

<br/><br/>
Example to run the code:
<br/>
<br/>
python summe_main.py --splits summe.yml

python tvsum_main.py --splits tvsum.yml


<br/><br/>

Thank for some open-source code from [VASNet](https://github.com/ok1zjf/VASNet),
[DR-DSN](https://github.com/KaiyangZhou/pytorch-vsumm-reinforce),
[DSNet](https://github.com/li-plus/DSNet),
[KTS Algorithm](https://github.com/pathak22/videoseg/tree/master/lib/kts),
[VSLNet](https://github.com/IsaacChanghau/VSLNet).

If there are any other questions, please contact jianghao@stu.pku.edu.cn.

